679
00:42:30,910 --> 00:42:33,119
Just think about
the Spring Morning case.

680
00:42:33,120 --> 00:42:34,710
Obviously, you are out of favor.

681
00:42:34,950 --> 00:42:36,400
On top of that, you are transferred.

682
00:42:36,430 --> 00:42:39,279
Otherwise,
you could've had first dibs on it.

683
00:42:39,280 --> 00:42:40,960
At least, it could be helpful for you.

684
00:42:43,430 --> 00:42:45,040
I don't need that.

685
00:42:48,580 --> 00:42:50,380
Silly.

686
00:42:53,910 --> 00:42:55,000
Hi.

687
