690
00:43:29,600 --> 00:43:32,440
You have been either working
or being with Migao these days.

691
00:43:33,430 --> 00:43:35,190
Won't your girlfriend get angry?

692
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:37,350
You know what it is about.

693
00:43:37,870 --> 00:43:39,310
Seriously?

694
00:43:39,640 --> 00:43:41,480
