00:44:39,160 --> 00:44:40,560
Can we talk?

707
00:44:41,800 --> 00:44:43,440
Is it about the work?

708
00:44:43,560 --> 00:44:46,350
If not, there is nothing else
we can talk about.

709
00:44:46,510 --> 00:44:47,630
